"n\">z</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">DecidablePred</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">smooth</span> <span class=\"n\">z</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span> <span class=\"kd\">by</span> <span class=\"n\">unfold</span> <span class=\"n\">smooth</span> <span class=\"bp\">;</span> <span class=\"n\">infer_instance</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
